Ping An Sells Stake in Value Partners, Terms Show

-- B y   F o x   H u
-- 
2011-04-28T10:40:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/ping-an-sells-stake-in-value-partners-term-sheet-shows-1-.html
(Corrects third paragraph of story originally published
April 27 to show that spokesman wasn’t immediately able to
comment.)  A Ping An Insurance Group Co. unit
is selling a stake in  Value Partners Group Ltd. (806)  for as much as
HK$367.2 million ($47 million), according to a term sheet sent
to investors today.  Ping An Life Insurance is selling 51 million shares at
HK$6.90 to HK$7.20 apiece, the terms show. Value Partners shares
closed at HK$7.58 today in  Hong Kong .  UBS AG (UBSN)  is managing the sale, the terms show. Rico Ngai, a
Hong Kong-based spokesman for Ping An, couldn’t immediately
comment on the transaction.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fox Hu in Hong Kong at 
 fhu7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Lagerkranser at 
 lagerkranser@bloomberg.net  